description: "A map of the northern coast of Java and the important port cities of Batavia (Jakarta) and Bantem (Banten). The web of lines is a rhumbline network, and shoals, reefs and bathymetry (sea depth) are marked, all to aid navigation."
title: "Nieurve Afteekeningh Van de Noord Küst = Van Java. Vertoonende de Reede Van Batavia en Bantan."
